Class OverlapCandidate

  • java.lang.Object
    • Issue
      • OverlapCandidate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class OverlapCandidate
extends Issue
    An OverlapCandidate is generated whenever two kin terms both seem to have valid definitions, but they both cover at least one kin type. This is a subclass of Issue and will be presented to the User for resolution when she does 'Get New Suggestions.'
